text: CSF Spartanii is a Moldovan football club based in Selemet, Moldova. They play in the Moldovan "A" Division, the second-level division of Moldovan football. Founded in Selemet in April 2018, CSF Spartanii is a continuation of the CF Sparta team from the same locality, that in the past played in Division A and Division B . In the 2018 season Spartanii won Division "B" South and was promoted to Division A. ==History== 2011 – foundation as CF "Sparta" Selemet 2018 – renamed in CSF Spartanii ==Achievements== *Divizia B : Winners (2): 2015-16, 2018 ==League history== {| class="wikitable" |-bgcolor="#efefef" !
